name: Upper Tree of Life 43
description: Part 43 of a 28 minute video (each part in a series of 11), these parts can be joined together to make the full 28 minute video (1440p,60fps). Upper Tree of Life is a Virtual Reality interpretation of an acrylic painting study on the Kabbalah Tree of Life. Called the Upper Tree of Life, this is the divine version of the Kabbalah Tree. Video capture of a VR painting using Tilt Brush and Open Brush, original music by Barry Chabala (barrychabala.bandcamp.com/   IG: @barry.chabala.roeba.recordings   Twitter: @BarryChabala). This is the last part of the 28 minute video. Anyone who collects all parts will receive the full video, the full audio and the VR file (viewable in Open Brush). Please contact me through my Twitter account if you collect all 43 parts!
